          <div class="typed-box"><span id="typed-text"></span><span class="cursor-blink">|</span></div>
          <p class="hero-description">Penetration Tester and Security Researcher focused on web application security, offensive security labs, attack surface analysis, and practical technical growth through hands-on testing and disciplined reporting.</p>
          <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="stat-card"><h3 data-counter="24">0</h3><p>Hands-on Security Labs</p></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><h3 data-counter="18">0</h3><p>Technical Portfolio Assets</p></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><h3 data-counter="100">0</h3><p>Relentless Learning Mode</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn-group">
            <a href="#projects" class="btn btn-primary magnetic"><i class="fas fa-diagram-project"></i> View Work</a>
            <a href="Medhat-Elbaz-CV.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline magnetic"><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Download CV</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline magnetic"><i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Contact</a>
          </div>
